---
import DigitalBackground from "../components/DigitalBackground.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "Q&A";
import PageHead from "../components/PageHead.astro";

---

<BaseLayout title={title}>
    <PageHead h1={title}/>

    Don’t want to build the press, and our prebuilt options aren’t enough! Make a custom request
Send Us a Custom Request
Email us at our own email service at ******@newimpression.com, or fill out this form. If you need some guidance on what to write to us, look below and find our guide on what we need to know from you.
<DigitalBackground>
    <div class="email-form">
        <h2>Send Me a Message</h2>
        <form name="contact" method="POST" netlify?>
            <div class="contact-sender-info">
                <div class="contact-name-box">
                    <label for="name" class="contact-label">Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="contact-input" required>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-email-box">
                    <label for="email" class="contact-label">Email:</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="contact-input" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-message-box">
                <label for="message" class="contact-label">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" class="contact-input" required></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-submit-box">
                <input type="submit" id="submit" value="Submit">
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</DigitalBackground>

</BaseLayout>
